name: PhiNesse Brush Short Shader Brush 17
short_description: The short shader brush features a small, soft brush head great for smudging out color along the lash line. Offers superb control when applying color to very small areas of the eye.
long_description: The short shader brush features a small, soft brush head great for smudging out color along the lash line. Offers superb control when applying color to very small areas of the eye.
